TEXT.S:
u niyadu' nu Sakul malaliki.
kakiliman nacila a labi misalukyaw atu minanam tu nutuas a dadiwkami i putah nu adidian a cacudadan,yu pisalakyawan nu inanay,minanam kaku tu lukyaw atu dadiw,mudadiway i nacila a ina,minanam kaku mutuktuk, mikihatyakaku mutuktuk kya a matimen,anuayaw anika laliki maydih kaku miladay mudadiw atu mukelidtu inanay. tuktuk
nilacul
